<p><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 宋体;"> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;最美五月，阳光灿烂，春风拂面，母亲节如约而至。5月9日，经济管理学院第33期入党积极分子学班于A10-112教室开展“纸短情长，光影留爱”母亲节主题活动，学员们借此契机，表达对母亲的爱。</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1747297108306.png" alt="1747297108306.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1747297108306.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 宋体;"> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;一、手工传情，折制专属心意</span></p><p><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 宋体;"> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;活动现场，班委与小组长带领学员们制作个性化信封。彩笔在信纸上勾勒出蝴蝶、星星等图案，同学们专注的神情中满是对母亲的爱意。折叠、粘贴、彩绘，一个个独一无二的信封承载着对母亲的悄悄话，成为连接亲子情感的“专属纽带”。</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1747297122655.png" alt="1747297122655.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1747297122655.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 宋体;"> &nbsp; &nbsp; 二、书信抒怀，书写感恩真情在特色卡片上，同学们执笔写下平日里羞于开口的肺腑之言。字迹或工整或灵动，字里行间满是对母亲辛劳的体谅、对亲情陪伴的珍视。一封封未寄出的信，成为青春岁月里最温暖的情感注脚。</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1747297135582.png" alt="1747297135582.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1747297135582.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 宋体;"> &nbsp; &nbsp; 三、光影定格，传递温暖祝福</span></p><p><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 宋体;"> &nbsp; &nbsp; 活动尾声，同学们手持信封合影留念，镜头定格下这充满温情的瞬间。随后，大家录制母亲节祝福视频，一句句“妈妈，我爱您”“愿您永远健康快乐”通过镜头传递，让感恩之心突破空间界限，化作献给母亲的暖心礼物。</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 宋体;"><strong>B240509童梓盈</strong></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1747297147350.png" alt="1747297147350.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1747297147350.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 宋体;"><strong>B240509杨紫焱</strong></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1747297155484.png" alt="1747297155484.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1747297155484.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 宋体;"><strong>B240507陈文杰</strong></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1747297166942.png" alt="1747297166942.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1747297166942.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 宋体;"><strong>B240511毛思彤</strong></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1747297180646.png" alt="1747297180646.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1747297180646.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 宋体;"><strong>B240511罗玲源</strong></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1747297198124.png" alt="1747297198124.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1747297198124.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 宋体;"><strong>B240504温思怡</strong></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1747297213155.png" alt="1747297213155.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1747297213155.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 宋体;"><strong>结语</strong></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 宋体;"> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;此次活动不仅为同学们提供了表达亲情的平台，更以实践育人的方式深化了感恩教育。未来，经济管理学院将持续加强对青年学生的感恩教育，在点滴行动中，让爱与责任成为青春最亮丽的底色。</span></p><p><br></p>